{"tid":1942823,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"黃色經濟圈就係黃色互屌圈 根本搞嚟就係哂氣","createTime":"2020-03-25T09:41:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T09:56:24.000Z","uid":61348,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ac5c9d22adc815b1163cc85fb146c67bd6a54dff","tid":1942823,"uid":61348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T09:41:26.000Z","msg":"第一你根本避免唔到用中國貨 上次食黃店有支付寶<br />\n<br />\n而且成個經濟圈造就不停鬥黃 我亦睇唔到共產黨因為黃圈<br />\n有咩損失<br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈有頭尾都係失敗 唔止冇用仲害左場運動<br />\n<br />\n係時候宣布黃圈停止集中精神搞其他野"},{"pid":"0cd3b0c2a78c668d03ed9fae7b61d35c5fa6059b","tid":1942823,"uid":177213,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T09:43:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勿回五毛</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qbSTfhm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqbSTfhm.png&h=c2c2455b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29cfe1d9f18c421becddc4baef30abe2e705198a","tid":1942823,"uid":76603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T09:43:43.000Z","msg":"支那共諜 拉"},{"pid":"daec0c2df608c585fa9fd58e7632c3971db5113f","tid":1942823,"uid":179409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T09:46:44.000Z","msg":"戇鳩五毛<br />\n黃圈仲發展緊<br />\n而最重要係維持抗爭意識<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"31a44e4d11ab6f8aa31faf5427df0049501ca09a","tid":1942823,"uid":61348,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T09:47:23.000Z","msg":"捉鬼撚孜來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa3e7ecb5b086c2e56933037f286491059a0fe0","tid":1942823,"uid":41861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T09:49:51.000Z","msg":"唔係互屌 係屌你咋傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ff883a84184e333908cead8369d26f6d34e065","tid":1942823,"uid":61348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1aa3e7